  "synopsis": "The only body cultivator in the nine realms was betrayed by his close friend Li Yunfei, and his body and soul disappeared. By chance, his soul remained immortal, and unexpectedly happened to Xiao Chen, a dying disciple of Qingyun Sect. After rebirth, Xiao Chen not only resurrected, but also awakened his supreme magical power. He also vowed to take back everything that belonged to him, and walked out on his own magical path as the \"Venerable God\".\n\n(Source: iQIYI, translated)",
